b.	notifying the concerned officials and employees of their accountabilities and demand for the immediate settlement of their outstanding Cash advances, including imposing sanctions or withholding of salaries in case of non-compliance, pursuant to the provisions of paragraph 9.3.2 and other pertinent provision of COA Circular No. 97-002.

