a. identify and coordinate with the funding agencies for the account Due from NGA’s for the immediate settlement of the outstanding balance;
b. enforce collection of the un-deposited collections and bank charges from the accountable officers;
c. require immediate liquidation by the former accountable officers of unsettled cash advances thru issuance of final demand letter, otherwise, enforce refund or other legal mode of settlements for their accountabilities;
